    "date": "2021-06-26T23:53:22Z",
    "text": "Comprehensive National Mercury Monitoring Act\n\nThis bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) to establish\u00a0a national mercury monitoring program. Under the program, the EPA must track and report on long-term changes of mercury concentrations in air, water, soil, and fish and wildlife.\u00a0In addition, the EPA must establish an online database for mercury data."
